title: Proxmox VE: Node Info
agents: proxmox_ve
catalog: os/misc
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors a Proxmox VE node's status and subscription status. The service state for each
 status can be individually configured in the ruleset (OK, WARN, CRIT). By default, node status
 "online" and subscription statuses "new" and "active" are considered OK, while other statuses
 trigger appropriate warning or critical states.
 It shows the node status, subscription status and time until expiration, Proxmox VE version and number of hosted VMs.

discovery:
 One service per system is created.
